snippet: Baltimore, which had already lost Dennis Pitta to a season-ending hip injury earlier in training camp, suffered another injury with Ed Dickson’s slight hamstring tear.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Baltimore Ravens tight end Ed Dickson will miss at least a week of practice with torn hamstring; other NFL developments noted.
lead_paragraph: Baltimore, which had already lost Dennis Pitta to a season-ending hip injury earlier in training camp, suffered another injury with Ed Dickson’s slight hamstring tear.

headline.main: Ravens, With Pitta Out, Lose Another Tight End
